{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_51_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 星見プロのお姉さん枠",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――遙子の誕生日企画　当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of Haruko's Birthday Project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1400.0000238,
          "startTime": 1.4000000238
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　テントが燃えてるじゃない！\n二人とも、早く消すわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! The tent’s on fire!\nYou two‚ let’s put it out—hurry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 7.1666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……隣のカップルのせいね\nキャンプファイヤー、派手に燃やしてたみたいだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… It’s that couple next to us.\nIt looked like they were making a crazy campfire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "恋も炎も燃え上がったって？\n他人のテントまで燃やしてんじゃないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Love and flames burn bright\"‚ huh?\nDon’t go setting other people’s tents on fire!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6000021617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 19.133335495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこんなことになっちゃったのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How in the world did this happen…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.133335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-01-night",
      "startTime": 19.9387299855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.200000151,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1285.8263414,
          "startTime": 25.4858264924
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 25.1666669448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふーん、ふん\n佐伯遙子のミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm hmm‚ hum♪\nSaeki Haruko’s Miracle☆Idol Birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3333353917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "やけにご機嫌じゃない。どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look very happy today‚ what's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0000020583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "とうとう、あの名物企画『ミラクル☆アイドル\nバースデー！』のお話をいただいたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ I was asked to do that famous project‚\n“Miracle☆Idol Birthday!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2333343744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルのやりたいことを\nなんでも叶えてくれるなんて、わくわくしない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a project that grants any wish an idol has!\nIsn’t it exciting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事だけど、結構自由にやらせてもらえるものね\n何するか決まったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although it is work‚ you have a lot of freedom.\nHave you decided what to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6666697423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "実は、この日のためにずっと考えてたことがあって\n莉央さん、私と一緒にキャンプに行かない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I’ve had something I really wanted to do for that day.\nRio-san‚ would you like to go camping with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4000028212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "え、私？\nうーん……キャンプねぇ、あんまり経験ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ me?\nHmm… Camping… I don’t have much experience with that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4666694879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あと他に、mihoさんも誘うつもりで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’m also planning on inviting miho-san――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2333361546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。どういう人選なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on. What’s the criteria for choosing members?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.300001804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "急だと戸惑っちゃうわよね。それなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s sudden‚ so you’re probably confused. Well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.366667962,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3581.759238400011,
          "startTime": 76.9484272004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、mihoさん！\nちょうど良かったわ！　私の誕生日企画に――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ miho-san!\nPerfect timing! I want to invite you for my――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2333483616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "よく分からないけど、断るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t really understand‚ but I’ll have to decline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.433355991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ～っ！　即答しなくてもいいじゃない\n私達、友達でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh?! You don’t have to answer right away.\nWe’re friends‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7666852553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "貴方と友達になった覚えはないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t remember becoming friends with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0000226577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "もう冷たいなぁ。でも話を聞いたら\nきっと参加したくなっちゃうわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so cold. But if you listen to what I have to say…\nyou’ll definitely want to participate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4000226577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "私の誕生日企画があってね、二人とキャンプに\n行きたいな～って考えてたの！　ね、素敵でしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a birthday project‚ and I was thinking it would be fun to go camping with you two!\nDon’t you think it’s a great idea?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6000226577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に説明を始めないで\nまず、このメンバーの意味が全く分からないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t just start explaining things on your own.\nFirst of all‚ I don’t understand the meaning of this member lineup at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7000226577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "それは私も気になりました\nお世辞にも仲がいい顔ぶれだとは思えないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was wondering about that too.\nTo be honest‚ I don’t think this is a group of people who get along well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9333559911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ほいほーい！　説明します！　私達って星見プロの中で\nカテゴリーとしてはお姉さん枠じゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ okay! I’ll explain! We’re all kind of considered\nthe “older sisters” of Hoshimi Pro‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2333559911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、歳が近いのにそんなに話したことないし\nちょっともったいない気がしてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ even though we’re close in age‚ we haven’t really talked that much‚\nso I thought it was kind of a waste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.4000226577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "このお仕事で一緒にキャンプに行けば\nもっと仲良くなれるかなー……なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we go camping together for this project‚\nmaybe we could get closer… or whatnot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7333559911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、今後同じ現場も増えるだろうし\nやりやすくなるかもしれないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is true that we will have more chances to work together‚\nso things would be easier if we get along but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6333559911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……特に必要性を感じないのだけど。それにkanaと\nfranも歳は近いわ。あの二人でいいじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don’t really see the need. Besides‚ kana and\nfran are close in age too. Wouldn’t they be better?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.1333783706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "も～、そういうことじゃないのよ\n私はmihoさんと莉央さんともっと仲良くなりたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ that’s not the point!\nI want to get closer to miho-san and Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.2666984797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……正直あまり気は進まないけど\n遙子のためだものね。私は参加させてもらうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…To be honest‚ I’m not really up for it…\nBut it’s for Haruko‚ so I’ll participate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3000297785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、ありがとう！\nmihoさんは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ thank you!\nWhat about you‚ miho-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.6333631118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "私は気が進まないから、断るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not interested‚ so I’ll decline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.2333570083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "むむむ……やっぱり一筋縄ではいかないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It really isn’t going to be easy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.900023675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "……あ！　そうよ、これだわ！\n私達、お姉さん枠以外にも共通点があると思うの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! Alright‚ this is it!\nI think we have something in common besides being the “older sisters”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.3666903417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "三人とも、アイドル業界の酸いも甘いも知る苦労人\nじゃない？　積もる話が沢山ある気がするのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve all been through a lot in the idol industry‚ haven’t we?\nI feel like we have a lot to talk about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.6666974624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "だから私、二人とは尺が足りなくなるまで\n話し込んじゃう自信があるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I’m confident that I could talk with you two\nuntil we run out of time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.0333763362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "百歩譲って、話が合いそうだとしても\nキャンプに行く必要はないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if we’ll get along well‚\nthere’s no need to go camping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.3667096695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないわ！　大自然は人を開放的にするのよ！\nお互いをさらけ出して、腹を割って話せばもっと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true! Nature makes people more open!\nIf we open up to each other and talk frankly‚ then――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.3333763362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "行く必要がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no need to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.4000501236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
