      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "ぎゃん！　なんで～？　行ってよ～！\nこうなったら絶対mihoさんに行ってもらうんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaat?! Whyyy?! Come ooon~!\nIf it comes to this‚ I’m absolutely taking miho-san with me!",
