      "startTime": 238.333383457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "やだ！　これを逃したら、一緒に行くチャンスなんて\nないもの！　あ、企画で行く所には穴場の秘湯が……",
