      "text": "十万部ぐらいですね。Web版もPV数が多い方ですし\nSNSでの宣伝もしっかりしてくれる雑誌です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About 100‚000 copies. The web version also has a high number of views‚\nand the magazine does a good job of promoting on social media.",
